install-tl.exe, install-tl.exe.sha256, install-tl.zip and
install-tl.zip.sha256 should have less suggestive (and different) names,
otherwise an absent minded user could click on (one of the)
"install-tl" (if extensions are hidden) instead of "install-tl-windows".

